data.description: Discover this fantastic 4-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom home in the sought-after Grayslake North High School district. It exudes contemporary charm with its wood laminate floors and intriguing custom details.  The kitchen effortlessly flows into the dining area, creating a comfortable and stylish living space.  The lower level adds versatility to the home, complete with a family room, cozy bedroom and an extra bathroom. Outside, this corner lot property is graced by a diverse array of mature trees in the front yard, offering a touch of seclusion. The rear of the house features a splendid deck, perfect for relaxation and hosting get-togethers, overlooking a generous backyard waiting for your creative touch. Plus, you'll have convenient access to the outdoor wonders of Miltmore and Fourth Lakes. This Lake Villa gem is ready for you to make it your own! Assumable VA Loan/Interest rate. Sellers will include 1 year home warranty!
